B040C022V035	40	22	35	and one of them, an expounder of the Law, asked Him as a test question,
B040C022V036	40	22	36	»Teacher, which is the greatest Commandment in the Law?«
B040C022V037	40	22	37	
        
B040C022V038	40	22	38	This is the greatest and foremost Commandment.
B040C022V039	40	22	39	And the second is similar to it: 
B040C022V040	40	22	40	The whole of the Law and the Prophets is summed up in these two Commandments.«
B040C022V041	40	22	41	While the Pharisees were still assembled there, Jesus put a question to them.
