B040C024V041	40	24	41	Two women will be grinding at the mill: one will be taken away, and one left behind.
B040C024V042	40	24	42	Be on the alert therefore, for you do not know the day on which your Lord is coming.
B040C024V043	40	24	43	But of this be assured, that if the master of the house had known the hour at which the robber was coming, he would have kept awake, and not have allowed his house to be broken into.
