B040C024V045	40	24	45	»Who therefore is the loyal and intelligent servant to whom his master has entrusted the control of his household to give them their rations at the appointed time?«
B040C024V046	40	24	46	Blessed is that servant whom his master when he comes shall find so doing!
B040C024V047	40	24	47	In solemn truth I tell you that he will give him the management of all his wealth.
