B040C025V026	40	25	26	»`You wicked and slothful servant,' replied his master, `did you know that I reap where I have not sown, and garner what I have not winnowed?«
B040C025V027	40	25	27	Your duty then was to deposit my money in some bank, and so when I came I should have got back my property with interest.
