B040C026V001	40	26	1	When Jesus had ended all these discourses, He said to His disciples,
B040C026V002	40	26	2	»You know that in two days' time the Passover comes. And the Son of Man will be delivered up to be crucified.«
B040C026V003	40	26	3	Then the High Priests and Elders of the People assembled in the court of the palace of the High Priest Caiaphas,
B040C026V004	40	26	4	and consulted how to get Jesus into their power by stratagem and put Him to death.
B040C026V005	40	26	5	But they said, »Not during the Festival, lest there be a riot among the people.«
