B041C005V015	41	5	15	and when they came to Jesus, they beheld the demoniac quietly seated, clothed and of sane mind– the man who had had the legion; and they were awe-stricken.
B041C005V016	41	5	16	And those who had seen it told them the particulars of what had happened to the demoniac, and all about the swine.
