B041C007V007	41	7	7	
        
B041C007V008	41	7	8	»You neglect God's Commandment: you hold fast to men's traditions.«
B041C007V009	41	7	9	»Praiseworthy indeed!« He added, »to set at nought God's Commandment in order to observe your own traditions!
B041C007V010	41	7	10	For Moses said, 
B041C007V011	41	7	11	But 
