B042C004V015	42	4	15	And He proceeded to teach in their synagogues, winning praise from all.
B042C004V016	42	4	16	He came to Nazareth also, where He had been brought up; and, as was His custom, He went to the synagogue on the Sabbath, and stood up to read.
