B042C004V038	42	4	38	Now when He rose and left the synagogue He went to Simon's house. Simon's mother-in-law was suffering from an acute attack of fever; and they consulted Him about her.
B042C004V039	42	4	39	Then standing over her He rebuked the fever, and it left her; and she at once rose and waited on them.
