B042C005V005	42	5	5	»Rabbi,« replied Peter, »all night long we have worked hard and caught nothing; but at your command I will let down the nets.«
B042C005V006	42	5	6	This they did, and enclosed a vast number of fish; and their nets began to break.
B042C005V007	42	5	7	So they signalled to their partners in the other boat to come and help them; they came, and they filled both the boats so that they almost sank.
