B042C006V016	42	6	16	James's relative Judas, and Judas Iscariot who proved to be a traitor.
B042C006V017	42	6	17	With these He came down till He reached a level place, where there was a great crowd of His disciples, and a multitude of people from every part of Judaea, from Jerusalem, and from the sea-side district of Tyre and Sidon, who came to hear Him and to be cured of their diseases;
B042C006V018	42	6	18	and those who were tormented by foul spirits were cured.
B042C006V019	42	6	19	The whole crowd were eager to touch Him, because power went forth from him and cured every one.
