B042C011V012	42	11	12	or if he asks for an egg, will offer him a scorpion?
B042C011V013	42	11	13	If you then, with all your human frailty, know how to give your children gifts that are good for them, how much more certainly will your Father who is in Heaven give the Holy Spirit to those who ask Him!«
