B042C011V015	42	11	15	But some among them said, »It is by the power of Baal-zebul, the Prince of the demons, that he expels the demons.«
B042C011V016	42	11	16	Others, to put Him to the test, asked Him for a sign in the sky.
B042C011V017	42	11	17	And, knowing their thoughts, He said to them, »Every kingdom in which civil war rages goes to ruin: family attacks family and is overthrown.
