B042C011V028	42	11	28	»Nay rather,« He replied, »they are blessed who hear God's Message and carefully keep it.«
B042C011V029	42	11	29	Now when the crowds came thronging upon Him, He proceeded to say, »The present generation is a wicked generation: it requires some sign, but no sign shall be given to it except that of Jonah.
