B042C011V043	42	11	43	Alas for you Pharisees! for you love the best seats in the synagogues, and you like to be bowed to in places of public resort.
B042C011V044	42	11	44	Alas for you! for you are like the tombs which lie hidden, and the people who walk over them are not aware of their existence.«
